  <text>
    <body>
      <div subtype="original" type="letter" xml:id="L.1131" xml:lang="it">
        <pb facs="#IMG.1" n="1"/>
        <dateline> Mil., 9. 4. 84.</dateline>
        <opener>Amico pregiatissimo. </opener>
        <p>Le so grado per il buon viso ch'Ella fa a' miei fogli. Jerlaltro Le mandai il resto di VII, 3<note n="1"
            place="foot" type="editorial">
            <hi rend="unknown"
            rendition="#none">AGI</hi> 7 (1880-83), terzo fascicolo.</note>; ma i fogli irlandesi non mi sono ancora capitati. <note
            n="2" place="foot" type="editorial"> Vgl. dazu <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.letter.1131">
057-00247</ref>.</note> Debbono però arrivare da un momento all'altro.</p>
        <p>Vivissime grazie pei 'Kreol. St., VI.'<note n="3" place="foot" type="editorial">
            <bibl>
              <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.bibliography#BIBL.299">Hugo Schuchardt: <hi rend="unknown"
                  rendition="#none">Kreolische Studien VI : Über das Indoportugiesische von Mangalore</hi>, in: <hi
                  rend="unknown" rendition="#none">Sitzungsberichte der philosophisch-historischen Klasse der kaiserlichen Akademie der Wissenschaften in Wien </hi>105 (1884), 881-904</ref>
            </bibl> (Brevier-/Archivnr. 150).</note> Ed ecco ch'Ella diventa per davvero un '<foreign xml:lang="de">weltumsegler</foreign>'!</p>
        <p>Anche il <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.languages#L.3104">friulano</ref> dice: <hi
            rend="unknown"
            rendition="#none">nardáis-si sintáis-si</hi>, 'guardátevi' 'sentátevi (=sedétevi), ecc. Confronti il Pirona<note
            n="4" place="foot" type="editorial">
            <bibl>
              <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.bibliography#BIBL.3191">Jacopo Pirona: <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">Vocabolario friulano</hi>
              </ref>
            </bibl>, Venezia, 1871.</note>, a p. LXVIII, e le 'Annotaz. soprslv.' p. 456 n<note n="5" place="foot" type="editorial">
            <bibl>
              <ref target="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.bibliography#BIBL.1927"> G. I. Ascoli: <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">Saggio di morfologia e lessicologia soprasilvana</hi>
              </ref>
            </bibl>, in: <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
AGI</hi> 7 (1880-83), 406-602.</note>, scrivendo le quali linee io appunto teneva dinanzi anche i paradigmi friulani.- //</p>
        <closer>
          <salute>Salute e buone vacanze!<lb/> Suo aff<hi rendition="#sup">mo</hi> div<hi rendition="#sup">mo</hi>
          </salute>
          <lb/>
          <signed>
            <persName ref="https://gams.uni-graz.at/o:hsa.persons#P.1056">
Asc.</persName>
          </signed>
        </closer>
        <postscript>
          <p>
            <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">sbrigáisi</hi> Arch. IV 297, 3<note n="6" place="foot" type="editorial">
              <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
AGI</hi> 4 (1878), 297, Zeile 3.</note>, <hi rend="unknown"
              rendition="#none">chiatáisi</hi> ib. ib. 14, <hi rend="unknown"
              rendition="#none">
inzenogláisi</hi> ib. ib. 40, <hi rend="unknown" rendition="#none">
svarbazáisi</hi> ib. 298, 7.</p>
        </postscript>
        <pb facs="#IMG.2" n="2"/>
      </div>
